➜乡情常常弥漫起伤感
http://www.sohu.com/a/425730355_100281316	23518
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201019/c1adcaafc7a64f42846e166857c713b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 斜阳脉脉，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 撒一地橘黄色的温暖，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 雾霭装饰着树林，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 雁阵在天际间淡远。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201019/fd18a64e4a1f415ab02337d74bbb243b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 秋虫渲染着傍晚的静谧，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 村庄流浪着缕缕炊烟，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 鸡犬长吟着寂寞，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 秋风吹出一身的疲倦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201019/b478997b04f74b4db445c854c3502665.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
